{
  "texts": [
    "This process can be early-stopped if the verifier outputs an identical action at any refinement step.",
    "Specifically, the i-th step initial action a 0 i is generated as the Eq. 6.",
    "Then, the verifier will refine the action based on the tool-wise experience:",
    "and the final refined result is chosen as the action of the current step:",
    "where j = 1, 2,..., n means the refinement step index, n is the max refinement step."
  ]
}